Implement a PWM duty cycle controller driven by ADC input:

```c
// PWM controller
typedef struct {
    uint32_t arr;      // auto-reload value (period)
    uint32_t ccr;      // capture/compare (duty)
} PWM;

void pwm_set_duty_percent(PWM* pwm, float duty_pct);
float pwm_get_duty_percent(const PWM* pwm);

// ADC averaging filter (removes noise)
