// IoT sensor node: temperature + BLE transmission

// Device behavior:
// Wake every 60 seconds:
//   - Wake up: 2ms at 20mA (clock init)
//   - Read ADC: 1ms at 10mA
//   - BLE transmit: 7ms at 15mA
//   - Total active: 10ms
// Sleep: 59.99 seconds at 5μA

// Average current calculation:
// Iactive = (2ms×20mA + 1ms×10mA + 7ms×15mA) / 10ms
//         = (40 + 10 + 105) / 10 = 15.5mA average while active
// Active duty = 10ms / 60000ms = 0.0167%
// Isleep = 5μA = 0.005mA

// Average current = (0.0167/100)×15.5mA + (99.983/100)×0.005mA
//                 = 0.00259mA + 0.00499mA
//                 = 0.00758mA ≈ 7.58μA average!

// Battery life:
// Battery = 1000mAh
// Life = 1000mAh / 0.00758mA = 131,926 hours
//      = 131,926 / 8760 = ~15 YEARS!

// Compare to always-on (no sleep): 1000/15.5 = 64 hours!
// Sleep modes give 15 years vs 64 hours = 2060x improvement!

printf("Average current: %.2f uA\n", 7.58);
printf("Battery life: %.1f years\n", 15.0);

